<h1><img src="/pub/Graphics/Icons/eff3d_white_icon.gif" ALT="">
<a name="top">EFF &quot;Legal Cases - Crypto - Bernstein v. US Dept. of State: Tien Declaration Exhibits&quot; Archive</a></h1>

<H5>http://www.eff.org/pub/Legal/Cases/Bernstein_case/Legal/Exhibits/Tien_declaration
</H5>



<h6>Last Updated Sun Oct 20 20:56:46 PDT 1996</h6><br>
<br>
   Exhibits filed with Lee Tien's declaration in support of the complaint 
<p>
<TABLE BORDER=4 CELLPADDING=4 CELLSPACING=4>
<TR ALIGN=CENTER>
<TD><A HREF="#files">Files</A></TD><h6></h6>
<TD><A HREF="#dirs">Subdirectories</A></TD><h6></h6>
