<DOCHDR>
http://kragar.eff.org:80/pub/Publications/John_Perry_Barlow/HTML/brooklyn_bridge.html 204.253.162.4 19970103143507 text/html 9259
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 03 Jan 1997 14:35:08 GMT
