<h1><img src="/pub/Graphics/Icons/eff3d_white_icon.gif" ALT="">
<a name="top">EFF &quot;Legal Cases - SPA v. ISP Lawsuits, and SPA 'ISP Code of Conduct'&quot; Archive</a></h1>

<H5>http://www.eff.org/pub/Legal/Cases/SPA_cases/
</H5>



<h6>Last Updated Mon Dec 09 11:24:08 PDT 1996</h6><br>
