<h1><img src="/pub/Graphics/Icons/eff3d_white_icon.gif" ALT="">
<a name="top">EFF &quot;Privacy - Crypto - Key Escrow 1995 (US): `Clipper II`&quot; Archive</a></h1>

<H5>http://www.eff.org/pub/Privacy/Key_escrow/Clipper_II/
</H5>



<h6>Last Updated Mon Aug 05 13:33:57 PDT 1996</h6><br>
