<h1><img src="/pub/Graphics/Icons/eff3d_trans_icon.gif" ALT="">
<a name="top">EFF &quot;Freedom of Information - UK&quot; Archive</a></h1>

<H5>ftp.eff.org/pub/Activism/FOIA/Foreign_and_local/UK/
<br>gopher.eff.org, 1/Activism/FOIA/Foreign_and_local/UK
<br>http://www.eff.org/pub/Activism/FOIA/Foreign_and_local/UK/
</H5>



