<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>EFF &quot;Privacy - Crypto - Pro-CODE, ECPA96 &amp; SAFE (`96 Crypto Legislation)&quot; Archive</TITLE><LINK REV="made" HREF="mailto:webmaster@eff.org"></HEAD>
