<a name="note"></a>

<h2><IMG SRC="/pub/Graphics/Icons/doc1_icon.gif" ALT=""> 
    Subject: A Note About This Newsletter</h2> 

To better serve our members and the interested public, <a 
href="http://www.eff.org">EFF</a> will be 
releasing its newsletter more frequently.  This has the dual benefit of 
getting news to you faster, and keeping the size of the newsletter small
and easier to digest in these times of "information overload".
<p>
If you have comments or questions about this newsletter or <a 
href="http://www.eff.org">EFF</a> in 
general, please send them to <a href="mailto:editor@eff.org">editor@eff.org</a> (Stanton McCandlish). 
<p>

<Return to the <a href="#menu> Table of Contents</a>

