<a name="list"></a>
<h2><IMG SRC="/pub/Graphics/Icons/doc1_icon.gif" ALT="">
LIST OF PARTICIPATING ORGANIZATIONS</h2>

In order to use the net more effectively, several organizations have
joined forces on a single Congressional net campaign to stop the
Communications Decency Act.
<p>
Please send a message to vtw@vtw.org with "send orgs" in the subject
line to receive a list of these organizations.
<p>
In alphabetical order:
<p>
<br>American Civil Liberties Union (ACLU) <a href="mailto:infoaclu@aclu.org">infoaclu@aclu.org</a>
<br>American Communication Association (ACA)  <a href="mailto:comminfo@cavern.uark.edu">comminfo@cavern.uark.edu</a>
