<li> <a href="http://www.eff.org/pub/EFF/calendar.eff">http://www.eff.org/pub/EFF/calendar.eff</a><p>

See also our new Now-Up-to-Date HTML calendar at:
<a href="http://events.eff.org">http://events.eff.org</a><p>

