<a name="nybbles"></a>
<h2><img src="http://www.eff.org/pub/Graphics/Icons/doc1_icon.gif" ALT="">
Subject: NewsNybbles</h2>

<a name="effchanges"></a>
<h2><img src="http://www.eff.org/pub/Graphics/Icons/doc1_icon.gif" ALT="">
Subject: New EFF Organizational Memberships</h2>

EFF now has two new membership categories:<p>
 
<li>- <b>Nonprofit/Educational/Library</b> - $100/year <br>
    Open to any not-for-profit NGO, or similar organization (e.g. in 
    countries that don't have official non-profit categories, or 
    organizations denied such status for political reasons 
    by hostile governments). Also open to schools and to libraries.<p>

<li>- <b>Corporate</b> - $5000<br>
    Please pledge your support, and help us make a difference!  This 
    category is for the large and small companies alike. If you'd like to 
    help out with larger contributions, donation of services or equipment, or
    with project cooperation, please contact us at <a href="mailto:ask@eff.org">ask@eff.org</a> or 
    +1 415 436 9333 (voice), +1 415 436 9993 (fax).<p>

For an EFF membership for (for fax, snail mail, email or upload), please see:<p>

<li>  <a href="http://www.eff.org/EFFdocs/join_eff.html">http://www.eff.org/EFFdocs/join_eff.html</a><br>
<li> <a href=" ftp://ftp.eff.org/pub/EFF/join.eff (login: anonymous)"> ftp://ftp.eff.org/pub/EFF/join.eff (login: anonymous)</a>   <br>
<li>  <a href="gopher://gopher.eff.org/1/EFF/join.eff">gopher://gopher.eff.org/1/EFF/join.eff</a><p>

