<BR><h2><A NAME="files">
<IMG SRC="/pub/Graphics/Icons/doc1_icon.gif" ALT=""></A>
Files in this Archive</h2>

A summary of the variety of Internet tools available out there.  Part of a project by John December to develop a categorization and taxonomy of Internet tools.  Most of the files below are gzipped parts of that summary; others are described below.

<DL>
<DT><a href="README"><B>README</B></a>
<DD>A more extended description of the summary.  Gives details about the various versions of the summary contained within this archive.
<DT><a href="internet-tools.col.gz"><B>internet-tools.col.gz</B></a>
<DD>No Description
<DT><a href="internet-tools.dat.gz"><B>internet-tools.dat.gz</B></a>
<DD>No Description
<DT><a href="internet-tools.dvi.gz"><B>internet-tools.dvi.gz</B></a>
<DD>No Description
<DT><a href="internet-tools.gif"><B>internet-tools.gif</B></a>
<DD>The Internet tools .gif.
<DT><a href="internet-tools.gz"><B>internet-tools.gz</B></a>
<DD>No Description
<DT><a href="internet-tools.html.gz"><B>internet-tools.html.gz</B></a>
<DD>No Description
<DT><a href="internet-tools.ps.gz"><B>internet-tools.ps.gz</B></a>
<DD>No Description
<DT><a href="internet-tools.tax"><B>internet-tools.tax</B></a>
<DD>About developing a taxonomy of Internet tools.
<DT><a href="internet-tools.tex.gz"><B>internet-tools.tex.gz</B></a>
<DD>No Description
<DT><a href="internet-tools.txt.gz"><B>internet-tools.txt.gz</B></a>
<DD>No Description
<DT><a href="internet-tools.use"><B>internet-tools.use</B></a>
<DD>How to use the Internet tools document.
</DL>

