<h1><img src="/pub/Graphics/Icons/eff3d_white_icon.gif" ALT="">
<a name="top">EFF &quot;Censorship - Internet Censorship Legislation - California&quot; Archive</a></h1>

<H5>http://www.eff.org/pub/Censorship/Internet_censorship_bills/Foreign_and_local/CA
</H5>



<h6>Last Updated Wed Oct 30 17:59:37 PDT 1996</h6><br>
<TABLE BORDER=4 CELLPADDING=4 CELLSPACING=4>
<TR ALIGN=CENTER>
